#: ../../user/downloading-installing-upgrading/upgrade/4_2.rst:3
#: d2138942ce934814bcb618331bb7324d
msgid "How to upgrade to Qubes 4.2"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/downloading-installing-upgrading/upgrade/4_2.rst:6
#: 3e312b35b973410ba47af8d370544565
msgid ""
"This page explains how to upgrade from Qubes 4.1 to Qubes 4.2. There are two"
" ways to upgrade: a clean installation or an in-place upgrade. In general, a"
" clean installation is simpler and less error-prone, but an in-place upgrade"
" allows you to preserve your customizations."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/downloading-installing-upgrading/upgrade/4_2.rst:9
#: 310acf149cd3426c82cec2c555f14eeb
msgid "Back up"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/downloading-installing-upgrading/upgrade/4_2.rst:12
#: e3cd0199b1c5442596756c9f818cfcca
msgid ""
"Before attempting either an in-place upgrade or a clean installation, we "
"strongly recommend that you first :doc:`back up your system </user/how-to-"
"guides/how-to-back-up-restore-and-migrate>` so that you don’t lose any data."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/downloading-installing-upgrading/upgrade/4_2.rst:15
#: 551220c425064ed38d388725c934c910
msgid "Clean installation"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/downloading-installing-upgrading/upgrade/4_2.rst:18
#: 838de58ccad744c69ccbbb27df63f396
msgid ""
"If you would prefer to perform a clean installation rather than upgrading "
"in-place:"
msgstr ""

