#: e431e13f365a44acb744be446718fd40
msgid ""
"Install the ``qubes-dist-upgrade`` tool. This is the inplace upgrade tool, "
"which is not what we’re doing. However it will be needed in order to prepare"
" the templates for the 4.2 version. You install it with the following "
"command in the dom0 terminal:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/downloading-installing-upgrading/upgrade/4_2.rst:30
#: dc06b646c7cc41758d911e74243410cd
msgid ""
"Change your templates to use the 4.2 repositories instead of the 4.1 ones. "
"You do this with the following command in the dom0 terminal:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/downloading-installing-upgrading/upgrade/4_2.rst:37
#: 60eb3ced36f448ca9f01b561b9ee75d8
msgid ""
"**Note**: This step is critical to ensure the templates will receive updates"
" once Qubes 4.1 reaches end-of-life (EOL) and was missing in previous clean "
"installation instructions."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/downloading-installing-upgrading/upgrade/4_2.rst:39
#: 6b5816dc5b334bc8bcab6f3e04aa0c13
msgid ""
"Create a :ref:`backup <user/how-to-guides/how-to-back-up-restore-and-"
"migrate:creating a backup>` of your current installation."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/downloading-installing-upgrading/upgrade/4_2.rst:41
#: 0ae3e760162e4f6196eb63c4130c0855
msgid ""
"`Download <https://www.qubes-os.org/downloads/>`__ the latest 4.2 release."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/downloading-installing-upgrading/upgrade/4_2.rst:43
#: 1f648c0f32864ce19ef58c115775f06b
msgid ""
"Follow the :doc:`installation guide </user/downloading-installing-"
"upgrading/installation-guide>` to install Qubes 4.2."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/downloading-installing-upgrading/upgrade/4_2.rst:45
#: 5e5fa5f22a9c42c9bf4f64c66b39ef16
msgid ""
":ref:`Restore from your backup <user/how-to-guides/how-to-back-up-restore-"
"and-migrate:restoring from a backup>` on your new 4.2 installation."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/downloading-installing-upgrading/upgrade/4_2.rst:50
#: 3fbbf73f6ab64465b8717f47ceda4016
msgid "In-place upgrade"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/downloading-installing-upgrading/upgrade/4_2.rst:53
#: 0264249561ce45d58620c0c2834bc6a9
msgid ""
"**Warning:** It is not possible to upgrade directly from releases earlier "
"than 4.1. If you’re still on an earlier release, please either perform a "
"`clean installation of 4.2 <#clean-installation>`__ or :doc:`upgrade to 4.1 "
"</user/downloading-installing-upgrading/upgrade/4_1>` first."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/downloading-installing-upgrading/upgrade/4_2.rst:55
#: 209b87458e394c45b725964d41b4e05b
msgid ""
"The upgrade may take several hours, and will download several gigabytes of "
"data."
msgstr ""

